{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4ed362991b","title":"三军革命派会审陈再道纪实","origin":"《打倒反革命修正主义分子——陈再道》　武汉钢二司武汉大学总部宣传部　毛泽东思想武汉军区政治部红旗总部合编　河南二七公社宣传部翻印　1967年9月","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"273cf12909","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":4,"articleId":"4ed362991b"}],"tags":[{"id":"0d8f653275","name":"武汉地区无产阶级革命派百万雄师联络站（百万雄师）","type":"人物"},{"id":"20ebde32a6","name":"王力","type":"人物"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4d9a2ea656","name":"陈再道","type":"人物"},{"id":"93cca4665d","name":"谢富治","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"6947f9d5e2","name":"陈再道"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"939862f7c5","type":"title","text":"三军革命派会审陈再道纪实","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"84cabce4b7","type":"authors","text":"陈再道","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"f1219120ce","type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民解放军各总部、国防科委、海陆空三军机关和文体单位无产阶级革命派八月四日斗争反革命分子——陈再道纪实","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"babca440dc","type":"paragraph","text":"八月四日下午，中国人民解放军各总部、国防科委、海陆空三军机关和文体单位无产阶级革命派部分代表斗争了武汉“7·20”暴乱事件的罪魁祸首反革命分子陈再道，陪斗的反革命分子钟汉华、牛怀龙（前独立师师长）、蔡炳臣（前独立师政委）、巴方庭（前湖北军区人武部长）。……，打得敌人狼狈不堪，昏头昏脑，又抹鼻涕又擦泪不知所措。初战告捷，大快人心，大长了无产阶级革命派的志气，大灭了敌人的威风，充分显示了三军革命造反派的强大战斗力。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"388a6a3e29","type":"paragraph","text":"“把反革命分子陈再道押上来！”会议负责同志的话刚落，会场上立即响起了一片“打倒刘、邓、陶！”“打倒陈再道！”等口号声，陈再道这些家伙见来势凶猛，只好乖乖地低头弯腰90度，吓得两腿不停打抖。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"9b3e04e42f","type":"paragraph","text":"三军造反派首先宣布：“陈再道你一手策划和制造了武汉军区‘7·20’反革命暴乱事件，犯下了滔天罪行，今天我们要跟你清算，你必须老实交待！”接着问陈再道：“7·20是什么事件？”","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"30fcaf2eed","type":"paragraph","text":"陈答：“我犯了罪，7·20是个反革命事件。”","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"8ddf2c2eef","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你根据什么说是反革命事件？”","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"ca50d82b85","type":"paragraph","text":"陈答：“反对毛主席派去的代表，那还不是反革命事件啊！但到底是谁煽动，我也知道。”这个老混蛋想大帽子下开小差，真是白日做梦！造反派代表大喝一声：“你这个混蛋，你老实交待你在这次事件中担当了什么角色？！”陈听了，豆大的汗珠直往下滚，连忙说：“我要承担责任，我，我……”","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"876c8b41f0","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你说，你有什么罪？！”","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"1d2295108b","type":"paragraph","text":"答：“我执行了刘、邓反动路线，一直顽固坚持，造成恶果。”","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"545b67fbf6","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你是怎样策划7·20事件的？”","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"23d53fc7dc","type":"paragraph","text":"陈狡辩说：“我没有策划。”","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"2d02f17397","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你承认有罪，罪在什么地方？”","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"85ba3a3f20","type":"paragraph","text":"陈答：“群众受了我们的欺骗，我们的蒙蔽，我们说我们没有犯方向路线的错误，这些都是错误的。”","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"d3789b9c0b","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你一手策划的7·20事件，你为什么说没有？”","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"28dc6aea95","type":"paragraph","text":"答：“我没有策划嘛！我跟谁说过？跟谁开过会？”……","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"c96dbaac7e","type":"paragraph","text":"口号声象千万发重炮弹向陈再道轰去……，一阵哭哭啼啼，连连求饶，这是陈贯彻始终的手法，在造反派的怒斥下，他就装着象个“可怜”的样子，哭哭啼啼，而且哭得很“伤心”，可是哭声再大，却一滴泪也没有。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"6214c8b241","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你老实不老实？！”","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"13bf870611","type":"paragraph","text":"答：“我怎么还不老实，我到这个时候还有什么话不能讲。”","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"dcaafcab93","type":"paragraph","text":"（这只老狗说的好听，就是死不交待。）","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"ded4be81fe","type":"paragraph","text":"问他怎么策划“7·20事件”的？他还是推说没有，并且说：“这个反革命事件里面有没有坏人在策划，我也说有人在策划。百万雄师独立师到底怎么一下子起来，我也弄不清楚，我也挨了他们的打。”","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"606dc0cc00","type":"paragraph","text":"“他们后来为什么不打你了？”造反派问道","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"dbf447da2b","type":"paragraph","text":"答：“我也不晓得他们要打就打，不打就不打。”","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"205cfda053","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你挨打时说了什么话？！”","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"48d56f93b5","type":"paragraph","text":"答：“我说你们这个要不得，你们犯法了。”","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"c0dab34163","type":"paragraph","text":"一位代表在场发言，陈挨打时喊：“我是陈再道，不是王力。”这时百万雄师才把他放了。原来百万雄师一些人之所以打陈再道是因为搞误会了。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"ec820202ea","type":"paragraph","text":"陈答：“我是坏蛋头子”","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"7e406a76e0","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你对中央代表说：我们的文化革命搞的不好，你们到街上看一看。这句话你讲了没有？！”","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"e76e25027f","type":"paragraph","text":"答：“讲了，讲了。”","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"d057a50143","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你要中央代表看什么？你是什么意思？你要达到什么目的？！”","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"0c2a5047b1","type":"paragraph","text":"答：“我那时候没有什么目的。”","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"0158f2c57f","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"69c192158f","type":"paragraph","text":"后来陈又说：“当时这个思想，就是说他们（指中央代表）光是看了几个造反派的情况，其它地方没有看，所以说你们到街上看看。”","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"a1a5467130","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你让中央代表去了解谁的情况？！”","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"a261847ac4","type":"paragraph","text":"答：“对其它组织，……，到红武兵，百万雄师去了解一下。”","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"413be00f0b","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你认为中央不了解百万雄师的什么情况？”","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"0e6a514bcc","type":"paragraph","text":"答：“我没想那些，我是让他们了解全部情况。”","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"0a2f3f6677","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你这是什么意思？”","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"fecb19ef93","type":"paragraph","text":"答：“意思就是说他们没有了解全面情况，我这就是对抗中央文革。”","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"1f1588ac1a","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你认为中央的指示是不全面的？”","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"8019f9ab51","type":"paragraph","text":"答：“是对中央了解武汉的情况不满，不是对中央决定不满。”","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"c425044118","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你要中央派去的代表到街上去看什么？街上都搞了些什么？”","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"347be60c19","type":"paragraph","text":"陈象脚踩住了刀子似的大叫大喊：“我可不知道街上发生了什么呀……”一位代表说：“中央代表到武汉的第二天他们就组织一场大规模的武斗。”陈却说没有这回事。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"ac42ce59cb","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“你怎么知道没有？！”","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"91d9ca76e2","type":"paragraph","text":"答：（无法抵赖，改口说：）“有，有。”","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"003d581810","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你为什么说没有？","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"0f8df086aa","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我是说16日没有大规模武斗，就是工总和电车站的打了一下。","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"93458f193b","type":"paragraph","text":"（鉴于陈态度恶劣，继续负隅顽抗，造反派代表向陈宣判：你让中央代表到街上看看，其目的是：第一……，第二……，事实俱在，陈不敢反抗。接着又向陈审问了第二个问题。）","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"4c7d4b918c","type":"paragraph","text":"问：总理到武汉后，你鼓动下边的干部，在师以上干部会议上给周总理提意见，有没有？","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"052dd2550b","type":"paragraph","text":"答：没有，没有。","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"e468875b95","type":"paragraph","text":"问：揭露出来怎么办？！","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"04427b9971","type":"paragraph","text":"答：揭露出来我认罪。……。","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"af6872abfe","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你在师以上干部会议上干了些什么？！","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"9b8c774792","type":"paragraph","text":"答：这个会议是在总理来以前开的，那时候对我们有指示，我们下面思想混乱，有的说《百万雄师》好，有的说三新、工总好，我们开个会，叫师的单位每个来两个人，我说把你们党委的意见拿出来，不要受军区框框的限制。有什么意见愿意怎么说就怎么说，然后写个东西，把各单位的意见综合起来，将跟北京谈判做个基础。","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"237dd43b45","type":"paragraph","text":"问：中央6、7月份对武汉地区文化大革命有过什么指示？！","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"eb19022c32","type":"paragraph","text":"答：制止武斗，对百万雄师有指示。要百万雄师撤兵。","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"09654d4134","type":"paragraph","text":"问：什么时间的指示？","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"beb689448f","type":"paragraph","text":"答？六月十日左右。","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"d89abaace9","type":"paragraph","text":"问：中央对百万雄师是支持还是批评？！","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"b6bedf63d1","type":"paragraph","text":"答：当然是批评。","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"6f0d8d0176","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你是支持还是反对百万雄师？！","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"a3ca34598f","type":"paragraph","text":"答：百万雄师我没有支持。……。没有明支持，我所作所为都是帮了百万雄师的。","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"f907d76e38","type":"paragraph","text":"问：中央对百万雄师的态度，你已经知道了，你还发动师以上的干部提自己的看法，以后好到北京和中央谈判，这是什么意思？！","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"b51c666bd7","type":"paragraph","text":"〔陈无言已对，低着头装死狗。〕","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"af9440d45e","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你在总理召集的师以上干部会议上，怎样挑动下面的干部给总理提意见？","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"4b1a2ffb1e","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我没有哇。","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"ce1af4d37d","type":"paragraph","text":"问：胡说！空军15军政委王新同志揭发你了！你煽动下面的干部在会上提意见，企图压中央改变态度，有没有？","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"41af248805","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我没有跟他讲，我怎么敢讲这个话呀！我的天，我想也不敢想呀！……革命造反派说：“人、物俱在，你休想赖掉。…”陈无言可答，狼狈不堪。","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"70e01dcf6a","type":"paragraph","text":"（又问第三个问题。）","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"536cc4959d","type":"paragraph","text":"问：谢副总理对你们讲：武汉地区的军队要支持真正的革命造反派，你是怎么回答谢副总理的？","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"a324e0ceb8","type":"paragraph","text":"答：当时我们说，我过去也是支持他们的。","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"542ee5bd68","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你支持谁？","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"711464c24c","type":"paragraph","text":"答：三新二司，我们过去也是支持三新二司，到现在支持的方针不变，那是我们党委的方针。","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"059594c615","type":"paragraph","text":"问：如果你是支持三新二司，那你为什么说，他们犯了方向路线错误呢？","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"8ad0f18753","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我们支持三新二司是以前，以后他们向我们进行斗争，我们现认识到错了。","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"16bd03bd26","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你怎么支持三新二司的？","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"dae7d84555","type":"paragraph","text":"答：现在看起来我们实际上是打击了造反派，我们以前也真正支持，现在打击是事实，以前支持也是事实。","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"f3bf578ba1","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你说，工总干的坏事二司干了，工总没干的二司也干了，有没有这回事？","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"5e243c80d1","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我讲了。（陈只得承认支持百万雄师。）","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"1db46e56f2","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你支持了百万雄师，你是不是想翻案？","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"b04bfc174f","type":"paragraph","text":"答：不翻案。","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"10c21bb50d","type":"paragraph","text":"（代表们又回头追问，陈是怎样对抗谢副总理指示，陈一口咬定说没有。）","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"448843a8cb","type":"paragraph","text":"一位代表揭发说：“谢副总理指示说，武汉地区军队要支持真正的革命造反派。”你说，“武汉只有一派，没有两派，你说了没有？”","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"47bbe259a0","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我什么时候讲过是一派呢？好几派嘛！","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"d87fc4a1a6","type":"paragraph","text":"问：上面问到你的这些做法都是对抗毛主席、党中央的，是不是？","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"a1d9d23e64","type":"paragraph","text":"答：是。","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"2c004356c4","type":"paragraph","text":"（问陈再道第四个问题是独立师绑架、围攻、殴打王力同志的经过。陈再道矢口否认自己的罪恶，拒不交待事情发生的经过。……专门审问了牛怀龙，一位代表揭发说：王力同志被绑架以后，陈再道却说不要怕群众嘛！这时他还带着老婆到东湖睡大觉，对这事实不敢承认，顽固抵赖。）","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"7c01b9131a","type":"paragraph","text":"同志们气极了说：“你这个老家伙，简直要带着脑袋进棺材。”","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"9195153d63","type":"paragraph","text":"陈再道对抗说：“进棺材吧！”","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"743683cc1c","type":"paragraph","text":"当问到是谁把周总理的指示传达给部队时，陈答：是蔡炳臣。","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"7dfd603dee","type":"paragraph","text":"问：是谁批准他传达的？","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"3d46513beb","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：我不知道。","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"49376627b2","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你是吃干饭的？！","index":93,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"cf1338dc4e","type":"paragraph","text":"……代表们警告陈：“你这是解放军的败类，现在武汉地区的军民起来造你的反了，你不要抱幻想了，你不要欺骗，那是妄想。”所以陈听说武汉军民造他的反连说：好，好。","index":94,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"a51926ac46","type":"paragraph","text":"问：他们为什么造你的反呢？","index":95,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"5750668e4a","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我执行了反动路线。","index":96,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"c457012174","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你不是支持三新二司吗？","index":97,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"e4169ecb7b","type":"paragraph","text":"答：那只是口头上说说。","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"9a42fc0d0c","type":"paragraph","text":"问：谁喊：“陈再道政权万岁”！","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"35c8ad4d45","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我不知道。","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"5a3f5cb190","type":"paragraph","text":"问：是不是百万雄师喊的。","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"ad74b61a35","type":"paragraph","text":"答：他们那么多人，我怎么知道？","index":102,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"2b8437b112","type":"paragraph","text":"问：他们就在你的跟前喊的，你怎么不知道。","index":103,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"2fe3d5a4ba","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我听也不敢听。","index":104,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"df34e90377","type":"paragraph","text":"问：毛主席教导我们，世上没有无缘无故的爱，也没有无缘无故的恨，百万雄师为什么那样爱你？","index":105,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"aa668be89d","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我也不要他们爱。","index":106,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"22d2b3f86d","type":"paragraph","text":"（紧接着三军造反派又审问了第五个问题。）","index":107,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"5b4720802a","type":"paragraph","text":"问：七月十日上午，你们开了一个会，你在会上讲了些什么？","index":108,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"4ecd3f3e0b","type":"paragraph","text":"答：讲武汉地区文化革命形势大好。","index":109,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"10c5dea644","type":"paragraph","text":"问：什么大好，你杀的人还少？！","index":110,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"f0313faf33","type":"paragraph","text":"答：报纸都那么讲大好，大好。","index":111,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"95a566e177","type":"paragraph","text":"问：还讲了什么？","index":112,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"6e4ee36903","type":"paragraph","text":"答：三新二司是造反派，犯了错误，要团结，要斗争，要他们转变，以后还要依靠。","index":113,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"8f378c2488","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你说三新二司天天打我们的战士，算什么鸡巴革命，说了没有？","index":114,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"9f22c45bf5","type":"paragraph","text":"答：没有。","index":115,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"4aeee81074","type":"paragraph","text":"（这时把蔡炳臣拉上来审问。）","index":116,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"3f3420acf8","type":"paragraph","text":"问：陈再道对三新二司怎么讲的？","index":117,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"3abbbc132d","type":"paragraph","text":"蔡答：七月十日，他们（指陈再道）召开了一个会，是驻武汉部队师以上干部参加的。我是牛怀龙传达的，陈再道首先讲了三新二司以前我们支持他们。现在天天搞我们部队，这算鸡巴革命派。……","index":118,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"bf9e8eb95f","type":"paragraph","text":"问：他说的对不对？","index":119,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"c3b188e4e4","type":"paragraph","text":"答：他讲的这些都是我讲的。","index":120,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"3ffb22b3b0","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你对百万雄师还有什么？","index":121,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"45dd0866ef","type":"paragraph","text":"（陈东拉西扯，根本不交待。）","index":122,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"3f1c66608a","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你在会上对大家说过，你们说百万雄师不好，但是群众都向着他们，干部亮相都亮在他们那里，百万雄师的大方向是正确的等等，说了没有？","index":123,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"b77601685a","type":"paragraph","text":"答：说了，说了。","index":124,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"6c722a4b93","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你亮相亮到那一边？","index":125,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"ca7e20b675","type":"paragraph","text":"陈一会说亮到毛主席革命路线一边，一会又说亮到邓、刘路线一边，一会又说亮在百万雄师一边。","index":126,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"da021fbac2","type":"paragraph","text":"问：你还说《百万雄师》这个组织，全国最少有的，不能再好了。","index":127,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"e454d02a78","type":"paragraph","text":"（陈先说不是这个意思，后来一听说要蔡炳臣来交待，他又连声说是这，是这。最后，三军造反派把陈再道、钟汉华、牛怀龙、巴万庭五个反革命分子一起带到台前，排成一排进行了集体宣判，这几个坏蛋，站在那里，丧魂落魄。","index":128,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"62878310ec","type":"paragraph","text":"三军革命造反派共提了以下三个问题，每个问题都勒令这三个坏蛋回答。）","index":129,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"ab84f4e9c4","type":"paragraph","text":"一、“7·20”武汉地区发生了绑架毛主席派去的代表谢富治、王力同志，这是什么性质的条件？","index":130,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"c6e338d44a","type":"paragraph","text":"陈答：是反革命事件。","index":131,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"f3318bc2d2","type":"paragraph","text":"钟答：是反革命暴乱事件，是反党反毛主席的。","index":132,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"49de164e8d","type":"paragraph","text":"蔡答：是个军事政变，矛头是对准毛主席派去的代表谢富治、王力、余立金同志。","index":133,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"2a47d5187b","type":"paragraph","text":"牛答：是反革命暴乱事件。","index":134,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"e676b1ad5c","type":"paragraph","text":"二、你们这一小撮人在这次反革命暴乱中扮演了什么角色？","index":135,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"6824900f23","type":"paragraph","text":"陈答：我是操纵者，我是这个反革命暴乱的罪魁祸首。","index":136,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"8586647708","type":"paragraph","text":"蔡答：我是凶手。","index":137,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"889438bede","type":"paragraph","text":"牛答：我扮演了陈、钟的帮凶的角色。","index":138,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"c7179be3af","type":"paragraph","text":"三、“7·20”事件，是你们这一小撮坏蛋长期反对党中央、反对毛主席和林副主席的一个暴露，你们武汉军区是一个反革命窝子，是不是这样？","index":139,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"3325be23d1","type":"paragraph","text":"陈等五个反革命分子供认武汉军区是个反革命窝子，并分别报了其它一些反革命分子名单。","index":140,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"a4bba7a728","type":"paragraph","text":"这次战斗近十个小时。","index":141,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"},{"id":"caedc51966","type":"appellation","text":"来源：《打倒反革命修正主义分子——陈再道》  武汉钢二司武汉大学总部宣传部  毛泽东思想武汉军区政治部红旗总部合编  河南二七公社宣传部翻印  1967年9月","index":142,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b"}],"page":{"id":"17abc20c31","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4ed362991b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}